Docker Network
1. Isloted Docker Network -> In which applications can interact with ech other but for application outside this needs to connect using the port number in it.

1. docker network ls : shows the list of network
2. docker network create mongo-create

Whatever is happening in the docker is inside the container the world outside the container doesnot know what is happening inside the container also cannot interact with the conatainer.

1. docker exec -it 60826e73c13c bash
2. docker stop : closes all when the work is done.
3. docker kill : no matter work done or not it will be killed.
